data.description: Discover the perfect blend of style and function in this 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem.  Two living areas, ideal for relaxation and entertainment, along with the flexibility of a formal dining space that could easily double as a home office.  Beautiful Kitchen , Spacious pantry with breakfast area. Great master suite featuring a walk-in closet and a luxurious 4-piece bath.  Updated laminate flooring and plush carpets , also updated central heating and air system. Stonebridge Patio home, with No HOA. This is your chance to experience refined living with practical design. Don't miss out—schedule a showing today and make this well-appointed Home your very own.
